svg.title: VdK
svg.desc: Credit platforms allow private and institutional investors to invest directly in personal or corporate loans. Businesses and consumers thus gain new access to finance. Thus, credit platforms improve the credit supply, promote financial participation and make a positive contribution to the economy. The Association of German Credit Platforms is committed to the professional, honest and transparent structuring of the lending platform business as well as to the adherence to the highest quality standards by all market participants.
